B.lyrics:
1. Babusisiwe, Bazakudla ilifa, abayanga, bazakudla ilifa, emoyeni, bazakudla ilifa.
Chorus:
Ngoba umbuso wezula`ungowabo.

2. Babusisiwe; abakhalayo; bazaduduzwa;
3. Babusisiwe; abamnene; bomelukulunga;
4. Babusisiwe; abalambela; bomelukulunga;
5. Babusisiwe; abalesihawu; bazahawukelwa.
(c / f Mat 5,1-12; Luka 6,20- 23) M. Majahana

M.lyrics:
Mama Mariya, Nkosikazi yokuthula
Mama wethu.
Siphe, ukuthula mama siphe ukuthula. (2x)
1. Nkosikazi eyetheswa, ngomqhele wenkanyezi;
2. Nina weNdodana kaNkulunkulu, xotsha inzondano lodlakela;
3. Sicelele ukuthula, emulini lelizweni lethu;
4. Mama ugcwele umusa, kuthokoza kwezulu lomhlaba;
5. Msizi wamakholwa, Mvikeli wabahluphekayo;
6. Kwathi igazi lichitheka, elizweni lethu sakhala kuwe;
7. Wahlenga amadodana, lamadodakazi engozini yokufa:
8. Mthombo wokulunga, kakha`owadelwa nguwe ecela`usizo;
9. Londoloza`iBandla, duduza abakhalayo, siza abagulayo;
10. Sivuse lapho sisiwa, qinisa ababuthakathaka; 11. Mama siyabonga, sicelele ukuthula, kumntanako
ukuthula. M. Chifana

U.lyrics:
Chorus:
UFransisi weAssisi wayeliqhawe lothando
lesibonelo somusa. (2x).
1. Wadela lumhlaba, ngenxa yokuthanda`uNkulunkulu;
Watshiya`abazali, wazinikela eNkosini.
waqoqa`abangane, baqalisa umhlangano.
2 Watshiya inotho, waba ngumuntukazana,
Konke ayelakho, wakupha abayanga;
Eyakhe inotho, kwakungumthandazo.
3. Wathanda imvelo, kwangathi ingumuntu;
Wayetshumayeza, inyoni zemkhathini;
Ngezidalwa zonke, wadumisa`uNkulunkulu4. Ngezenzo zakhe,wathandeka eNkosini;
INkosi yambusisa, yamupha`amanxeba ayo; Olwakhe udumo, lwadlula`olwamakhosi.
A. Gwenelo

W.lyrics:
1. Wozani bantwana, wozani masinya; simbone uJesu uKristu iNkosi. Ovela`ezulwini, ofika`emhlabeni; ulethe uxolo lomusa lobuhle.
2. Simbone uJesu, elela`emgwembeni; simbone luMntwana, omuhle oNgcwele. Wozani sithabe, sithokozisise;
simbone uJesu uMntwana omuhle.

3. E! nanga`uMariya; emkhonza uJesu; ethaba embona uMntwana omuhle; loJosefa`oNgcwele, embonga luMntwana; odlula`izithunywa ngobuhle lomusa.
4. Zwanina`izithunywa, zicula ingoma; zimkhonza luMntwana olela`emkhonjeni. Bonana`abelusi beguqa kuJesu;
bethaba ngokuba kuzela`uMsindisi.
5. Ke lathi sithanda luMntwana omuhle; Simkhonza, simbonga ngengoma ezinhle. Simnika`inhliziyo, ahlale nje kizo;
ahlale kakuhle angaba`esatshiya.
